[section#mdspan.sub.overview
    [:en] Overview
    [:zh_CN] 概述
]

[para]
[:en] The [`submdspan] facilities create a new [`mdspan] viewing a subset of
elements of an existing input [`mdspan].
[:zh_CN] [`submdspan] 设施创建一个新的 [`mdspan]，用于查看一个现存输入 [`mdspan]
中的元素的一个子集。

[:en] The subset viewed by the created [`mdspan] is determined by the
[`SliceSpecifier] arguments.
[:zh_CN] 由 [`SliceSpecifier] 各实参确定所创建的 [`mdspan] 所查看的子集。

[para]
[:en] Given a signed or unsigned integer type [`IndexType], a type [$S] is a
[+[`submdspan] slice type for [`IndexType][%[`submdspan][!slice type for [`IndexType]]]]
if at least one of the following holds:
[:zh_CN] 给定一个有符号或无符号整数类型 [`IndexType]，如果至少满足下列条件之一，
则类型 [$S] 是[+对 [`IndexType] 的 [`submdspan] 分片类型[%[`submdspan][!对 [`IndexType] 的分片类型]]]:

[list]
[item]
[:en] [`is_convertible_v<[$S], full_extent_t>] is [`true];
[:zh_CN] [`is_convertible_v<[$S], full_extent_t>] 为 [`true]；

[item]
[:en] [`is_convertible_v<[$S], IndexType>] is [`true];
[:zh_CN] [`is_convertible_v<[$S], IndexType>] 为 [`true]；

[item]
[:en] [$S] is a specialization of [`extent_slice] and
[`is_convertible_v<[$X], IndexType>] is [`true] for [$X] denoting
[`[$S]::offset_type], [`[$S]::extent_type], and [`[$S]::stride_type];
[:zh_CN] [$S] 是 [`extent_slice] 的特例，并且 [`is_convertible_v<[$X], IndexType>] 对于
代表 [`[$S]::offset_type]、[`[$S]::extent_type] 和 [`[$S]::stride_type] 的 [$X] 都为 [`true]；

[item]
[:en] [$S] is a specialization of [`range_slice] and
[`is_convertible_v<[$X], IndexType>] is [`true] for [$X] denoting type of
[`[$S]::first], [`[$S]::last], and [`[$S]::stride] members; or
[:zh_CN] [$S] 是 [`range_slice] 的特例，并且 [`is_convertible_v<[$X], IndexType>] 对于
代表成员 [`[$S]::first]、[`[$S]::last] 和 [`[$S]::stride] 的类型的 [$X] 都为 [`true]；或者

[item]
[:en] all of the following hold:
[:zh_CN] 以下各项均成立：
 [list]
 [item]
[:en] the declaration [`auto `[...ls`] = std::move(s);] is well-formed
for some object [`s] of type [$S],
[:zh_CN] 对于某个类型为 [$S] 的对象 [`s]，声明式 [`auto `[...ls`] = std::move(s);] 是良构的，
 [item]
[:en] [`sizeof...(ls)] is equal to 2, and
[:zh_CN] [`sizeof...(ls)] 等于 2，并且
 [item]
[:en] [`(is_convertible_v<decltype(std::move(ls)), IndexType> && ...)] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`(is_convertible_v<decltype(std::move(ls)), IndexType> && ...)] 为 [`true]。
 [list:end]
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] Given a signed or unsigned integer type [`IndexType], a type [$S] is a
[+canonical [`submdspan] index type for [`IndexType][%[`submdspan][!canonical index type for [`IndexType]]]]
if [$S] is either [`IndexType] or [`constant_wrapper<v>] for some value [`v]
of type [`IndexType], such that [`v] is greater than or equal to zero.
[:zh_CN] 给定一个有符号或无符号整数类型 [`IndexType]，如果 [$S] 是 [`IndexType]
或者是某个类型为 [`IndexType] 的值 [`v] 的 [`constant_wrapper<v>]，且 [`v] 大于或等于零，
则 [$S] 是[+对 [`IndexType] 的规范 [`submdspan] 索引类型[%[`submdspan][!对 [`IndexType] 的规范索引类型]]].

[para]
[:en] Given a signed or unsigned integer type [`IndexType], a type [$S] is a
[+canonical [`submdspan] slice type for [`IndexType][%[`submdspan][!canonical slice type for [`IndexType]]]]
if exactly one of the following is [`true]:
[:zh_CN] 给定一个有符号或无符号整数类型 [`IndexType]，如果恰好满足下列条件之一，
则 [$S] 是[+对 [`IndexType] 的规范 [`submdspan] 分片类型[%[`submdspan][!对 [`IndexType] 的规范分片类型]]].

[list]
[item]
[:en] [$S] is [`full_extent_t];
[:zh_CN] [$S] 为 [`full_extent_t]；

[item]
[:en] [$S] is a canonical [`submdspan] index type for [`IndexType]; or
[:zh_CN] [$S] 是对 [`IndexType] 的规范 [`submdspan] 索引类型；或者

[item]
[:en] [$S] is a specialization of [`extent_slice] where all of the following hold:
[:zh_CN] [$S] 是 [`extent_slice] 的特例，并且以下各项均成立：
 [list]
 [item]
[:en] [`S::offset_type], [`S::extent_type], and [`S::stride_type] are
all canonical [`submdspan] index types for [`IndexType]; and
[:zh_CN] [`S::offset_type]、[`S::extent_type] 和 [`S::stride_type] 都是
对 [`IndexType] 的规范 [`submdspan] 索引类型；并且
 [item]
[:en] if [`[$S]::stride_type] and [`[$S]::extent_type] are both specializations
of [`constant_wrapper], then [`[$S]::stride_type::value] is greater than zero.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`[$S]::stride_type] 和 [`[$S]::extent_type] 都是 [`constant_wrapper] 的特例，
则 [`[$S]::stride_type::value] 大于零。
 [list:end]
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] A type [`S] is a [+:adj collapsing[!slice type]] if it is
neither [`full_extent_t] nor a specialization of [`extent_slice].
[:zh_CN] 如果类型 [`S] 既不是 [`full_extent_t]，也不是 [`extent_slice] 的特例，
则它是[+:adj 折叠[!分片类型]]。
[begin:note]
[:en] Each collapsing slice type in [`submdspan_mapping][=s] parameter pack
of slice specifier types reduces the rank of the result of [`submdspan_mapping] by one.
[:zh_CN] [`submdspan_mapping][=s] 分片说明符类型参数包中的每个折叠分片类型
都将 [`submdspan_mapping] 的结果的秩减少一。
[end:note]

[para]
[:en] A type [`S] is a [+:adj unit-stride[!slice type]] if
[:zh_CN] 如果类型 [`S] 满足下列条件，则它是[+:adj 单位跨步[!分片类型]]:
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`S] is a specialization of [`extent_slice] where [`S::stride_type] is a
specialization of [`constant_wrapper] and [`S::stride_type::value] is equal to 1, or
[:zh_CN] [`S] 是 [`extent_slice] 的特例，且 [`S::stride_type] 是
[`constant_wrapper] 的特例，并且 [`S::stride_type::value] 等于 1；或者
[item]
[:en] [`S] denotes [`full_extent_t].
[:zh_CN] [`S] 代表 [`full_extent_t]。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] Given an object [`e] of type [`E] that is a specialization of [`extents], and
an object [`s] of type [`S] that is a canonical [`submdspan] slice type for [`E::index_type],
the [+[`submdspan] slice range of [`s] for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`e]
[%[`submdspan][!slice range of [`s] for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`e]]]] is:
[:zh_CN] 给定 [`extents] 的特例 [`E] 类型的对象 [`e]，以及对 [`E::index_type] 的
规范 [`submdspan] 分片类型 [`S] 类型的对象 [`s]，则
[+对 [`e] 的第 [$k] 个尺度的 [`s] 的 [`submdspan] 分片范围
[%[`submdspan][!对 [`e] 的第 [$k] 个尺度的 [`s] 的分片范围]]]:

[list]
[item]
[:en] [=range([$0],e.extent([$k]))] if [`S] is [`full_extent_t];
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`S] 为 [`full_extent_t]，则为 [=range([$0],e.extent([$k]))]；
[item]
[:en] [=range(E::index_type(s.offset),E::index_type(s.offset))], if [`S] is a
specialization of [`extent_slice] and [`E::index_type(s.extent)] is zero; otherwise
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`S] 是 [`extent_slice] 的特例且 [`E::index_type(s.extent)] 为零，则为
[=range(E::index_type(s.offset),E::index_type(s.offset))]；否则
[item]
[:en] [=range(E::index_type(s.offset),E::index_type(s.offset + 1 + (s.extent - 1) * s.stri)],
if [`S] is a specialization of [`extent_slice]; otherwise
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`S] 是 [`extent_slice] 的特例，则为
[=range(E::index_type(s.offset),E::index_type(s.offset + 1 + (s.extent - 1) * s.stri)]；否则
[item]
[:en] [=range(E::index_type(s),[$[`E::index_type(s)] + 1])].
[:zh_CN] 为 [=range(E::index_type(s),[$[`E::index_type(s)] + 1])]。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] Given a type [`E] that is a specialization of [`extents], a type [`S] is a
[+valid [`submdspan] slice type for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`E]
[%[`submdspan][!valid slice type for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`E]]]]
if [`S] is a canonical slice type for [`E::index_type], and for [$x] equal to
[`E::static_extent([$k])], either [$x] is equal to [`dynamic_extent]; or
[:zh_CN] 给定 [`extents] 的特例类型 [`E]，如果类型 [`S] 是对 [`E::index_type] 的规范分片类型，
且对于等于 [`E::static_extent([$k])] 的 [$x]，要么 [$x] 等于 [`dynamic_extent]；
要么满足以下条件，则 [`S] 是[+对 [`E] 的第 [$k] 个尺度的有效 [`submdspan] 分片类型
[%[`submdspan][!对 [`E] 的第 [$k] 个尺度的有效分片类型]]]：

[list]
[item]
[:en] if [`S] is a specialization of [`extent_slice], then
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`S] 是 [`extent_slice] 的特例，那么
 [list]
 [item]
[:en@~] [$o] is less than or equal to [$x];
[:zh_CN@~] [$o] 小于或等于 [$x]；
 [item]
[:en@~] [$e] is less than or equal to [$x];
[:zh_CN@~] [$e] 小于或等于 [$x]；
 [item]
[:en@~] if [$e] is greater than one, then [$t] is greater than zero,
[:zh_CN@~] 如果 [$e] 大于一，则 [$t] 大于零，
 [item]
[:en@~] if [$e] is greater than zero, then [$o + 1 + (e - 1) * t] is less than or euqal to [$x],
[:zh_CN@~] 如果 [$e] 大于零，则 [$o + 1 + (e - 1) * t] 小于或等于 [$x]，
 [list:end]
[:en@~] where
[:zh_CN@~] 其中
 [list]
 [item]
[:en@~] [$o] is the value of [`S::offset_type::value] if [`S::offset_type] is
a specialization of [`constant_wrapper] and [`0] otherwise,
[:zh_CN@~] 当 [`S::offset_type] 是 [`constant_wrapper] 的特例时，[$o] 为
[`S::offset_type::value] 的值，否则为 [`0]，
 [item]
[:en@~] [$e] is the value of [`S::extent_type::value] if [`S::extent_type] is
a specialization of [`constant_wrapper] and [`0] otherwise,
[:zh_CN@~] 当 [`S::extent_type] 是 [`constant_wrapper] 的特例时，[$e] 为
[`S::extent_type::value] 的值，否则为 [`0]，
 [item]
[:en@~] [$t] is the value of [`S::stride_type::value] if [`S::stride_type] is
a specialization of [`constant_wrapper] and [`1] otherwise; and
[:zh_CN@~] 当 [`S::stride_type] 是 [`constant_wrapper] 的特例时，[$t] 为
[`S::stride_type::value] 的值，否则为 [`1]；以及
 [list:end]
[item]
[:en] if [$S] is a specialization of [`constant_wrapper], then [`S::value] is less than [$x].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [$S] 是 [`constant_wrapper] 的特例，则 [`S::value] 小于 [$x]。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] Given an object [`e] of type [`E] that is a specialization of [`extents] and
an object [`s] of type [`S], [`s] is a [+valid [`submdspan] slice for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`e]
[%[`submdspan][!valid slice for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`e]]]] if
[:zh_CN] 给定 [`extents] 的特例 [`E] 类型的对象 [`e] 和 [`S] 类型的对象 [`s]，
如果满足以下条件，则 [`s] 是[+对 [`e] 的第 [$k] 个尺度的有效 [`submdspan] 分片
[%[`submdspan][!对 [`e] 的第 [$k] 个尺度的有效分片]]]：

[list]
[item]
[:en] [`S] is a valid [`submdspan] slice type for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`E];
[:zh_CN] [`S] 是对 [`E] 的第 [$k] 个尺度的有效 [`submdspan] 分片类型；
[item]
[:en] the [$k^\text{th}] interval of [`e] contains the [`submdspan] slice range of [`s]
for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`e]; and
[:zh_CN] [`e] 的第 [$k] 个区间包含 [`s] 对 [`e] 的第 [$k] 个尺度的 [`submdspan] 分片范围；并且
[item]
[:en] if [`S] is a specialization of [`extent_slice], then:
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`S] 是 [`extent_slice] 的特例，则：
 [list]
 [item]
[:en@~] [`s.extent] is greater than or equal to zero, and
[:zh_CN@~] [`s.extent] 大于或等于零；并且
 [item]
[:en@~] either [`s.extent] is less than two or [`s.stride] is greater than zero.
[:zh_CN@~] 要么 [`s.extent] 小于二，要么 [`s.stride] 大于零。
 [list:end]
[list:end]
